I"Z=<p>Yesterday at the Silicon Valley GTUG meetup, I gave a presentation introducing the IndexedDB API.  I’ve thrown the slides on Slideshare, but the transcription there is absolutely miserable.  I’ll reproduce it here in a readable format, and add a few notes where appropriate.</p>

